"问题：", "marks": [{"type": "strong"}]}, {"type": "text", "text": "当前Pacvue每日导出数据到Google Sheets时，会创建新标签页，导致客户需手动合并标签页或构建复杂变通方案以形成单一数据集，自动化报告困难且耗时。"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "背景：", "marks": [{"type": "strong"}]}, {"type": "text", "text": "客户使用My Report的Send to (Google Sheets)功能进行每日自动化导出，需要数据连续输入到一个表格中，以便与Google Looker Studio等报告工具集成。"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "业务影响：", "marks": [{"type": "strong"}]}, {"type": "text", "text": "这使得自动化报告变得困难且耗时，特别是在月度或持续报告中，Looker Studio期望一个稳定、单页的数据源。"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "期望：", "marks": [{"type": "strong"}]}, {"type": "text", "text": "暂无描述"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": []}, {"type": "blockCard", "attrs": {"url": "https://pacvue-enterprise.atlassian.net/browse/PIN-2219"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "需求要点"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "问题：", "marks": [{"type": "strong"}]}, {"type": "text", "text": "报告模板中的日期列以文本格式而非日期格式生成，导致无法按日期排序，只能按字母顺序排序。"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "背景：", "marks": [{"type": "strong"}]}, {"type": "text", "text": "客户广泛使用报告，发现许多报告模板存在此问题。"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "业务影响：", "marks": [{"type": "strong"}]}, {"type": "text", "text": "影响客户在Excel中对日期列进行排序的功能，降低报告使用效率。"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "期望：", "marks": [{"type": "strong"}]}, {"type": "text", "text": "修复所有报告中日期列的格式，使其符合亚马逊日期格式要求。"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": []}, {"type": "blockCard", "attrs": {"url": "https://pacvue-enterprise.atlassian.net/browse/PIN-2215"}}, {"